程序包 ch.uzh.ifi.seal.changedistiller.model.entities

  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    AbstractHistory
    Abstract class for aggregating versions (StructureEntityVersion) of a source code entity (i.e. a class, a method or an attribute).
    AttributeHistory
    Attribute histories store change data about the history of an attribute.
    ClassHistory
    Class histories store change data about the history of a class.
    Delete
    Source code change that represents the delete of an entity.
    Insert
    Source code change that represents the insert of an entity.
    MethodHistory
    Method histories store change data about the history of an method.
    Move
    Source code change that represents the move of an entity.
    SourceCodeChange
    General (abstract) representation of a source code change.
    SourceCodeEntity
    Source code entity representing one particular AST node.
    StructureEntityVersion
    A structure entity version consists of all SourceCodeChanges applied in a version of an attribute, a class, or a method.
    Update
    Source code change that represents the update of an entity.
